                      ],
                      "text": "剧情预告-「惟余旧忆」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/23/237301566/68227850eb221e54dc2b6c91f89e1436_291937187263281196.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年6月2日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "转危为安后，众人纷纷离去，或心生幽思，或得偿所愿。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "惟有魈邀你一叙，向你讲述了一段夜叉的回忆…",
